r onBind(Intent intent) {     return null; } } </code></pre>  <p>From activity I could recieve that path. But I cannot create Bitmap by </p>  <pre><code>BitmapFactory.decodeFile(path); </code></pre>  <p>And I also tried with Picasso and Universal Imageloader to read that. There also I am getting NULL . </p>  <p>Please Help me..... </p>  <p>**sorry for my bad english</p>